&lt;p&gt;ap√≥s concluir o processo de autentica√ß√£o, o cliente armazena o JWT (stored token) e, nas pr√≥ximas requests, ir√° envi√°-lo via header, por &lt;a href=&quot;../API-REST/par√¢metros-das-APIs#header-parameters&quot; class=&quot;internal alias&quot; data-slug=&quot;API-REST/par√¢metros-das-APIs&quot;&gt;authorization parameters&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
