&lt;p&gt;se o token estiver correto, a request √© conclu√≠da. caso contr√°rio, a API retorna erro &lt;a href=&quot;../API-REST/status-HTTP#4xx-erro-de-client&quot; class=&quot;internal alias&quot; data-slug=&quot;API-REST/status-HTTP&quot;&gt;401 Unauthorized&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&quot;expira√ß√£o-e-refresh-token&quot;&gt;expira√ß√£o e refresh token&lt;a role=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-no-popover href=&quot;#expira√ß√£o-e-refresh-token&quot; class=&quot;internal&quot;&gt;&lt;svg width=&quot;18&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot; fill=&quot;none&quot; stroke=&quot;currentColor&quot; stroke-width=&quot;2&quot; stroke-linecap=&quot;round&quot; stroke-linejoin=&quot;round&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;como medida de seguran√ßa, o token expira depois de um determinado tempo. √© poss√≠vel implementar um &lt;em&gt;refresh token&lt;/em&gt;, que solicita um novo token quando o atual expira, evitando a necessidade de enviar as credenciais novamente.&lt;/p&gt;
