&lt;h2 id=&quot;implementa√ß√£o&quot;&gt;implementa√ß√£o&lt;a role=&quot;anchor&quot; aria-hidden tabindex=&quot;-1&quot; data-no-popover href=&quot;#implementa√ß√£o&quot; class=&quot;internal&quot;&gt;&lt;svg width=&quot;18&quot; height=&quot;18&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 24 24&quot; fill=&quot;none&quot; stroke=&quot;currentColor&quot; stroke-width=&quot;2&quot; stroke-linecap=&quot;round&quot; stroke-linejoin=&quot;round&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M10 13a5 5 0 0 0 7.54.54l3-3a5 5 0 0 0-7.07-7.07l-1.72 1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M14 11a5 5 0 0 0-7.54-.54l-3 3a5 5 0 0 0 7.07 7.07l1.71-1.71&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;para criar um algoritmo de busca ordenada, o exemplo utilizar√° &lt;em&gt;arrays&lt;/em&gt;: tipo de objeto que guarda uma sequ√™ncia de valores em uma mesma vari√°vel, em posi√ß√µes consecutivas. as posi√ß√µes s√£o numeradas a partir do &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.6444em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;a fun√ß√£o &lt;code&gt;binarySearch()&lt;/code&gt; recebe dois argumentos: um array ordenado &lt;code&gt;list&lt;/code&gt; e um n√∫mero inteiro &lt;code&gt;item&lt;/code&gt;. se o item estiver na lista, a fun√ß√£o ir√° retornar a posi√ß√£o onde ele est√° armazenado.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;o primeiro passo dessa fun√ß√£o √© verificar se a lista est√° vazia; caso esteja, retorna -1 e encerra a execu√ß√£o.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;caso a lista tenha tamanho &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.5782em;vertical-align:-0.0391em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mrel&quot;&gt;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mspace&quot; style=&quot;margin-right:0.2778em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.6444em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, a execu√ß√£o segue e s√£o declaradas duas vari√°veis de n√∫meros inteiros:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;low&lt;/code&gt; representa a posi√ß√£o mais baixa em que a busca ser√° realizada. √© iniciada com valor de &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.6444em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; pois a primeira busca √© feita na lista inteira;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;code&gt;high&lt;/code&gt; representa a posi√ß√£o mais alta em que a busca ser√° realizada. √© iniciada com tamanho da lista &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;‚àí&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; para compreender todas as posi√ß√µes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ent√£o, se inicia um la√ßo de repeti√ß√£o &lt;code&gt;while&lt;/code&gt;, que ir√° se repetir enquanto o valor mais baixo for menor que o valor mais alto. dentro desse la√ßo, √© inicializada a vari√°vel &lt;code&gt;mid&lt;/code&gt;, respons√°vel por definir a m√©dia entre as posi√ß√µes &lt;code&gt;low&lt;/code&gt; e &lt;code&gt;high&lt;/code&gt;, que ir√° representar a posi√ß√£o do primeiro chute (vari√°vel &lt;code&gt;guess&lt;/code&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;se o valor do chute &lt;code&gt;guess&lt;/code&gt; for igual ao valor do &lt;code&gt;item&lt;/code&gt;, o algoritmo encontrou a posi√ß√£o correta, por meio da fun√ß√£o &lt;code&gt;guessEqualsItem()&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;caso contr√°rio, ir√° testar se o n√∫mero do chute √© maior que o item, na fun√ß√£o &lt;code&gt;guessGreaterThanItem()&lt;/code&gt;. em caso afirmativo, atribui √† vari√°vel &lt;code&gt;high&lt;/code&gt; o valor do meio da lista &lt;code&gt;mid&lt;/code&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;‚àí&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. assim, a pr√≥xima tentativa j√° se iniciar√° excluindo a segunda metade da lista, pois j√°  se sabe que o valor √© &lt;em&gt;menor&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;caso o valor do chute seja menor do que o item,  condi√ß√£o que √© testada pela fun√ß√£o &lt;code&gt;guessLessThanItem()&lt;/code&gt;, √© atribu√≠do √† vari√°vel &lt;code&gt;high&lt;/code&gt; o valor do meio da lista &lt;code&gt;mid&lt;/code&gt; &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.7278em;vertical-align:-0.0833em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, excluindo toda a primeira metade da lista, pois j√° se sabe que o valor √© &lt;em&gt;maior&lt;/em&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;como estamos dentro de um la√ßo de repeti√ß√£o, a pr√≥xima execu√ß√£o ir√° acontecer com o n√∫mero de possibilidades reduzido pela metade, e assim por diante at√© que seja encontrado o valor de &lt;code&gt;item&lt;/code&gt; na lista.&lt;/p&gt;
