&lt;p&gt;as duas equa√ß√µes descrevem a mesma rela√ß√£o entre os n√∫meros &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.6444em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.6444em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; e &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.6444em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;16&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;, em que &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.6444em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; √© a base e &lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.6444em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;mord&quot;&gt;4&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; √© o expoente. a diferen√ßa √© que a &lt;strong&gt;equa√ß√£o exponencial isola a pot√™ncia&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;span class=&quot;katex&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;katex-html&quot; aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;base&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;strut&quot; style=&quot;height:0.6444em;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;