&lt;p&gt;¬†‚Äúqualquer elemento,¬†&lt;a href=&quot;https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Motivo_(m%C3%BAsica)&quot; title=&quot;Motivo (m√∫sica)&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;motivo&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;external-icon&quot; style=&quot;max-width:0.8em;max-height:0.8em&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;¬†ou pequena pe√ßa musical que originou alguma¬†&lt;a href=&quot;https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Varia%C3%A7%C3%A3o_(m%C3%BAsica)&quot; title=&quot;Varia√ß√£o (m√∫sica)&quot; class=&quot;external&quot;&gt;varia√ß√£o&lt;svg aria-hidden=&quot;true&quot; class=&quot;external-icon&quot; style=&quot;max-width:0.8em;max-height:0.8em&quot; viewBox=&quot;0 0 512 512&quot;&gt;&lt;path d=&quot;M320 0H288V64h32 82.7L201.4 265.4 178.7 288 224 333.3l22.6-22.6L448 109.3V192v32h64V192 32 0H480 320zM32 32H0V64 480v32H32 456h32V480 352 320H424v32 96H64V96h96 32V32H160 32z&quot;&gt;&lt;/path&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;&lt;/a&gt;¬†se torna um &lt;em&gt;tema&lt;/em&gt; a partir desse momento.‚Äù ‚Äî &lt;em&gt;Encyclop√©die Fasquelle&lt;/em&gt;, 1958&lt;/p&gt;
